public enum GpsStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<GpsStatus>

Enum to identify various GPS status the MMF may send. They include:

  • GPS_AVAILABLE
  • GPS_NOT_AVAILABLE
  • GPS_NON_TRACKABLE

Enum Constant Summary
GPS_AVAILABLE
          GPS is available on the phone and the MMF app has locked on a location.
GPS_NON_TRACKABLE
          This workout selected on the MMF app is non-trackable, such as a gym workout, so GPS data such as distance, speed, etc, will not be shown.
GPS_NOT_AVAILABLE
          The Android Location Services are turned on, but the MMF app has yet to lock on a location.

GPS_NON_TRACKABLE

This workout selected on the MMF app is non-trackable, such as a gym workout, so GPS data such as distance, speed, etc, will not be shown. The user of this SDK may which to show the user a dialog. The MMF app will show a dialog if the app is opened.
